{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"ok0e729ho7o09xetujkxc0m","title":"Financial","desc":"","updated":1704282636529,"created":1667694740818,"custom":{},"fname":"fin","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"a74e236173a03a7c1321b04842ad4c27","links":[],"anchors":{"collections":{"type":"header","text":"Collections","value":"collections","line":8,"column":0,"depth":2},"stock":{"type":"header","text":"Stock","value":"stock","line":14,"column":0,"depth":2},"sector-allocations-in-the-sp-500-index":{"type":"header","text":"Sector Allocations in the S&P 500 Index","value":"sector-allocations-in-the-sp-500-index","line":16,"column":0,"depth":3},"site":{"type":"header","text":"Site","value":"site","line":37,"column":0,"depth":2},"금리-급상승":{"type":"header","text":"금리 급상승","value":"금리-급상승","line":44,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["t5fywqwue0d669wrbr175s1","mnfr5aawf9823wg52eioe5a","1mdnrgagu4jotdgfc95tpsl","1lz392kfgmwh4kttirpj8tu","5cemmsbak2h71w8w2wflc3o","fjgotjrq215614fkstn84zc"],"parent":"Iy0MoL0KnL55Br3AfTS2C","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"financial\">Financial<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#financial\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"collections\">Collections<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#collections\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://thetaoofwealth.wordpress.com/2013/02/17/harry-brownes-17-golden-rules-of-financial-safety/\">Harry Browne’s 17 Golden Rules of Financial Safety</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://kr.investing.com/analysis/article-200445547\">변동성 높은 시장을 헤쳐나가기 위한 필수 투자 원칙 10가지</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://youtube.com/watch?v=Vkhzi1Zegfg\">시장은 합리적지만 가끔 비이성적 - 49:16</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"stock\">Stock<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#stock\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"sector-allocations-in-the-sp-500-index\">Sector Allocations in the S&#x26;P 500 Index<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#sector-allocations-in-the-sp-500-index\"></a></h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.etf.com/sections/etf-strategist-corner/sector-sector-sp-500\">https://www.etf.com/sections/etf-strategist-corner/sector-sector-sp-500</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>As of 12/31/2020</p>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>S&#x26;P 500 Index Sectors</th><th>Current Sector Weight</th><th>Vanguard Sector ETF</th><th>SPDR Sector ETF</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Information Technology</td><td>27.6%</td><td><a href=\"https://www.etf.com/vgt\">VGT</a></td><td><a href=\"https://www.etf.com/xlk\">XLK</a></td></tr><tr><td>Health Care</td><td>13.5%</td><td><a href=\"https://www.etf.com/vht\">VHT</a></td><td><a href=\"https://www.etf.com/xlv\">XLV</a></td></tr><tr><td>Consumer Discretionary</td><td>12.7%</td><td><a href=\"https://www.etf.com/vcr\">VCR</a></td><td><a href=\"https://www.etf.com/xly\">XLY</a></td></tr><tr><td>Communication Services</td><td>10.8%</td><td><a href=\"https://www.etf.com/vox\">VOX</a></td><td><a href=\"https://www.etf.com/xlc\">XLC</a></td></tr><tr><td>Financials</td><td>10.4%</td><td><a href=\"https://www.etf.com/vfh\">VFH</a></td><td><a href=\"https://www.etf.com/xlf\">XLF</a></td></tr><tr><td>Industrials</td><td>8.4%</td><td><a href=\"https://www.etf.com/vis\">VIS</a></td><td><a href=\"https://www.etf.com/xli\">XLI</a></td></tr><tr><td>Consumer Staples</td><td>6.5%</td><td><a href=\"https://www.etf.com/vdc\">VDC</a></td><td><a href=\"https://www.etf.com/xlp\">XLP</a></td></tr><tr><td>Utilities</td><td>2.8%</td><td><a href=\"https://www.etf.com/vpu\">VPU</a></td><td><a href=\"https://www.etf.com/xlu\">XLU</a></td></tr><tr><td>Materials</td><td>2.6%</td><td><a href=\"https://www.etf.com/vaw\">VAW</a></td><td><a href=\"https://www.etf.com/xlb\">XLB</a></td></tr><tr><td>Real Estate</td><td>2.4%</td><td><a href=\"https://www.etf.com/vnq\">VNQ</a></td><td><a href=\"https://www.etf.com/xlre\">XLRE</a></td></tr><tr><td>Energy</td><td>2.3%</td><td><a href=\"https://www.etf.com/vde\">VDE</a></td><td><a href=\"https://www.etf.com/xle\">XLE</a></td></tr><tr><td>TOTAL # OF HOLDINGS</td><td>(as of 12/31/2020)</td><td>2,561</td><td>518</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<h2 id=\"site\">Site<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#site\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4574652-sl-green-grab-a-near-8-percent-monthly-yield\">https://seekingalpha.com/article/4574652-sl-green-grab-a-near-8-percent-monthly-yield</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.fss.or.kr/fss/lifeplan/lifeplanIndex/index.do?menuNo=201101\">통합연금포털</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://dis.kofia.or.kr/websquare/index.jsp?w2xPath=/wq/rtrpsn/DISRtrPsnCmsnRate.xml&#x26;divisionId=MDIS02009003000000&#x26;serviceId=SDIS02009003000\">금융투자협회 전자공시서비스 퇴직연금 수수료율</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://tradingeconomics.com/\">Trading Economics</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"금리-급상승\">금리 급상승<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#금리-급상승\"></a></h2>\n<p>은행은 금리가 높을 수록 이득을 얻을 수 있으나 급상승의 경우에는 보유한 채권이 급락. 유동성이 늘어나지만 대출은 줄어듬</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://youtu.be/AH6q2PR--Gk?t=203\">https://youtu.be/AH6q2PR--Gk?t=203</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<hr>\n<strong>Children</strong>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/mnfr5aawf9823wg52eioe5a\">Cycle</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/1lz392kfgmwh4kttirpj8tu\">PER - 주가수익비율</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/5cemmsbak2h71w8w2wflc3o\">ROE - 자기자본이익률</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/fjgotjrq215614fkstn84zc\">Tax</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/1mdnrgagu4jotdgfc95tpsl\">The Long Term Behaviour of Leveraged ETFs</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/t5fywqwue0d669wrbr175s1\">전설적인 투자자들이 전하는 검증된 투자 철학 10가지</a></li>\n</ol>","noteIndex":{"id":"Iy0MoL0KnL55Br3AfTS2C","title":"Luke","desc":"","updated":1719298470122,"created":1644449449778,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"f